creator: Various
description:
LibriVox recording of Short Poetry Collection 157 by Various.
Read in English by Amy Gramour; Leonard Wilson; Craig Campbell; Sonia; Newgatenovelist; John Burlinson; Shakira Searle; Tomas Peter; annanneass; Son of the Exiles; Nancy Strickland
This is a collection of 22 poems read by LibriVox volunteers for June 2016.
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
